oc:kn_179763c5 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating or updating tasks via the ClickUp API" ;
    oc:directiveContent "ClickUp priorities are numeric: 1=Urgent, 2=High, 3=Normal, 4=Low. Time estimates must be specified in milliseconds. Due dates should be Unix timestamps in milliseconds." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Incorrect data types and formats will cause API errors or silent misconfigurations in automations." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_3d575097 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up or restructuring a ClickUp workspace" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Design ClickUp workspaces following the hierarchy: Workspace → Space → Folder → List → Task → Subtask. Keep the hierarchy shallow to maintain navigability." ;
    oc:hasRationale "A well-structured hierarchy enables efficient task organization, filtering, and reporting across teams." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_9729c468 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before executing any ClickUp automation skill operations" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Verify ClickUp API access and workspace permissions before attempting any automation. Confirm that the target Space, Folder, and List IDs are correct and accessible." ;
    oc:hasRationale "ClickUp API calls will fail silently or with cryptic errors if the authenticated user lacks workspace access or targets invalid resource IDs." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_a698e92f a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring ClickUp workspace automation rules" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use built-in automations to reduce manual overhead: auto-assign on task creation, due date reminders, status change workflows, and subtask-completion triggers." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Automations eliminate repetitive manual actions and ensure consistent process enforcement across the team." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_a777767e a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating or modifying lists and task statuses" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Avoid inconsistent status names across lists within the same Space. Standardize statuses to ensure automations and views work correctly." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Inconsistent statuses break automation triggers that rely on status names and create confusion in cross-list views and dashboards." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_ac2a87cc a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:WorkflowStrategy ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When connecting ClickUp with external tools" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Configure integrations (Slack, GitHub) to create bidirectional sync: Slack for notifications and quick commands, GitHub for branch/PR status linking back to tasks." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Bidirectional integrations keep context flowing between tools, reducing context-switching and ensuring task status reflects actual development progress." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

